Package net.proteusframework.internet.support.xml

XML support code.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AreaTagListener
    Externalizes internal AREA links.
    FormActionTagListener
    Externalizes form actions from their internal representation.
    HTMLNoEndTagListener
    Does not output end tags for certain elements such as "br" and "hr".
    IFRAMETagListener
    Externalizes internal IFRAME links.
    LinkTagListener
    Externalizes internal links and creates anchors and other types of links from their internal representation.
    RequestResponseTagListener
    Tag listener for generic parsing code that writes directly to a response.
    RequestResponseTagListenerConfiguration
    Configuration for RequestResponseTagListener.
    ScriptTagListener
    Special handling of script tags.
    URLTagListener
    Helper for URL based tags.
